08 gen -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-- ACCENTS IN ITALIAN:
we have two accents:
--> ACCENTO ACUTO: (è) -> will stress the sound of the word in an acute way: Tè (tea)
--> ACCNTO GRAVE (é) -> will stress with a lower sound. only exists with E (perché, poiché)


